Class ProcessInstanceSearchDescriptor

  • java.lang.Object

  • public class ProcessInstanceSearchDescriptor
extends ProcessInstanceSearchDescriptor
    Search descriptors are used to filter / sort results of a generic search.
    ProcessInstanceSearchDescriptor defines the fields that can be used as filters or sort fields on List<ProcessInstance> returning methods.
